ScrollList_GetItemText
#include Style
#Background wimp 1
Module:	<Window=>window/m>
#Line
#Wrap off
Veneer:	<scrolllist_get_item_text>
Syntax:	ScrollList_GetItemText
#indent

On Entry:
#indent 6
{FCode}r0 = flags
r1 = window object Id
r2 = 0x401a + 11 (16421)
r3 = gadget id
r4 = pointer to buffer
r5 = size of buffer
r6 = item
{f}
#indent
On exit:
#indent 6
{FCode}r5 = size of buffer (if r4=0)
     else r4 points to text.
{f}
#indent
#Wrap
Purpose:	Method gets the text of a scrolllist entry.